OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1779909062
OL,3,CCost of agency nurses triples in six
OL,4,Cyears
OL,6,FThe amount of money spent on agency
OL,7,Fnursing staff in Northern Ireland has
OL,8,Ftripled in six years.
OL,10,FHealth and Social Care Trusts spent
OL,11,F#162 million on agency nurses in the
OL,12,Fyear between 2024 and 2025.
OL,14,FIn the same year, some hourly rates
OL,15,Fpaid to nurses exceeded those paid to
OL,16,Ftheir counterparts in London.
OL,18,FThe findings were published in a
OL,19,Freport by Northern Ireland's
OL,20,FComptroller and Auditor General on
OL,21,FWednesday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1779909062
OL,3,CCost of agency nurses triples in six
OL,4,Cyears
OL,6,FThe report by Dorinnia Carville also
OL,7,Fshowed the annual costs for permanent
OL,8,Fnursing (and midwifery staff) reached
OL,9,F#1.1 billion between 2024 and 2025.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, health trusts spent #258
OL,12,Fmillion on temporary nursing (and
OL,13,Fmidwifery) staff in the same period.
OL,15,FThere was a 45% decrease in nurse
OL,16,Fvacancies between March 2019 and March
OL,17,F2025.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1779909062
OL,3,CCost of agency nurses triples in six
OL,4,Cyears
OL,6,FThe registered nursing workforce
OL,7,Fincreased from around 14,000-17,000
OL,8,Fwhole time equivalent nurses in that
OL,9,Fperiod, but the report found
OL,10,Fpersisting challenges.
OL,12,FParticular concerns were highlighted
OL,13,Faround a growing and costly reliance
OL,14,Fon agency staff.
OL,16,FOver #160 million was spent on agency
OL,17,Fnursing staff in 2024-25, with
OL,18,Fexpenditure levels having tripled
OL,19,Fsince 2018-2019.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1779909062
OL,3,CCost of agency nurses triples in six
OL,4,Cyears
OL,6,FAn agency nursing framework introduced
OL,7,Fin 2023, helped to largely eliminate
OL,8,Fthe use of expensive off-contract
OL,9,Fnursing agencies, the report found.
OL,11,FHowever, agency rates included in the
OL,12,Fframework, were substantially higher
OL,13,Fthan in England, including London.
OL,15,FSome maximum hourly rates for Band 5
OL,16,Fagency nurses were at least 35% higher
OL,17,Fin Northern Ireland than in most of
OL,18,FEngland, but could be up to 64% higher
OL,19,Fin some cases.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1779909062
OL,3,CCost of agency nurses triples in six
OL,4,Cyears
OL,6,FAgency nursing remained significantly
OL,7,Fmore expensive than other temporary
OL,8,Fnursing solutions.
OL,10,FAgency nursing staff cost #11 per hour
OL,11,Fmore, on average, than staff employed
OL,12,Fthrough the internal bank system used
OL,13,Fby trusts.
OL,15,FThe figures on total temporary staff
OL,16,Fexpenditure included both private
OL,17,Fsector agency staff and staff sourced
OL,18,Ffrom Trusts' internal bank system.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1779909062
OL,3,CCost of agency nurses triples in six
OL,4,Cyears
OL,6,FWeaknesses in workplace planning were
OL,7,Falso identified. Despite reduced
OL,8,Fnursing vacancies, the report found
OL,9,Fthat vacancy data does not fully
OL,10,Freflect workforce need.
OL,12,FThe number of reported registered
OL,13,Fnursing vacancies at March 2025
OL,14,F(1,178) reflected the number of funded
OL,15,Fjob roles being actively recruited.
OL,17,FHowever, the Department for Health
OL,18,Festimated that an additional 2,195
OL,19,Fnurses would be required to ensure
OL,20,Fsafe and effective staffing levels.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1779909062
OL,3,CCost of agency nurses triples in six
OL,4,Cyears
OL,6,FThe report also found limited evidence
OL,7,Funderpinning decisions on
OL,8,Fcommissioning nursing training places
OL,9,Fwith adequate workforce planning
OL,10,Fabsent.
OL,12,FSpeaking on the findings, the
OL,13,FComptroller and Auditor General said
OL,14,Fthe use of temporary staff is
OL,15,F"inevitable to some degree" but it
OL,16,Fmust be "planned and managed
OL,17,Feffectively to ensure the long-term
OL,18,Fsustainability of services".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1779909062
OL,3,CCost of agency nurses triples in six
OL,4,Cyears
OL,6,FDorinnia Carville said the new agency
OL,7,Fframework "delivered some important
OL,8,Fimprovements" but agency costs
OL,9,Fremained high and "better value for
OL,10,Fmoney could be achieved".
OL,12,FThe report recommended that "clear and
OL,13,Ftargeted action is taken by the
OL,14,FDepartment to reduce agency nursing
OL,15,Fusage and expenditure," she said.
OL,17,F"Improved workforce planning is also
OL,18,Frequired to identify workforce needs
OL,19,Fand establish a sufficient pipeline of
OL,20,Fappropriately skilled staff.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1779909062
OL,3,CCost of agency nurses triples in six
OL,4,Cyears
OL,6,F"This should entail greater use of
OL,7,Fmore cost-effective solutions such as
OL,8,Finternal bank staff, as well as more
OL,9,Faccurate and complete workforce data."
OL,11,F"We have also recommended that the
OL,12,FDepartment considers actions and
OL,13,Fapproaches taken to tackle these
OL,14,Fissues in other UK jurisdictions such
OL,15,Fas Scotland and Wales.
OL,17,FThe Department for Health said the
OL,18,Freport "recognises the progress" made
OL,19,Fin recent years to end the use of off-
OL,20,Fcontract agency nurses
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1779909062
OL,3,CCost of agency nurses triples in six
OL,4,Cyears
OL,6,FThey said expenditure on agency staff
OL,7,Fwas incurred to "ensure that safe and
OL,8,Feffective services can be sustained".
OL,10,FA planning group was established to
OL,11,Fimproved how staff are used, with the
OL,12,Faim of "reducing unsustainable agency
OL,13,Fand locum spend" across trusts.
OL,15,FThe Department said that agency use in
OL,16,FSocial Work was "entirely eliminated".
OL,18,FThey added that "significant progress"
OL,19,Fwas made in recent years to stabilise
OL,20,Fand grow the HSC workforce.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
